{
  "stem": "5883.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he told him, the building is big.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We might be hiding someplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when it got dark, we went home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that-- life went on like this for a long time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then once they took us to work on a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a barn where we stayed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were a big group of women and men in that barn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were supposed to work a whole week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when it came by the end of the week, like a Thursday, one of the women who made that water soup for us in the kitchen, when we were eating, she said to me quietly that the next day after we finished working-- that's gonna be Friday-- they gonna blow up the building with us together.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If anybody wants to run or do something about it, to let her know, she'll help.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that night when we got back to the barn to sleep, I got everybody together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I sat and I told them what the woman said.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't believe that it's gonna happen, and everybody will go home, you know, and all that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I told them, I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I have to die, doesn't matter if I die in the barn or if I die on the road.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just gotta take that chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So next morning when we went for the cup of water with the bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I told the woman I'm ready to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she had a long skirt from you-- that shawl like those, you know, farmers would wear there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got dressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took me on the horse and wagon just out of the-- that little station.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
